 C     O     D     E     S     T     A     T     D

+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
  daemon analyzing your attention & effect on code
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

You put to task of analyzing any of your supported language codebase
  providing the build/test action to be performed.
And it will keep a check on it at desired intervals mapping state of
  errors/warnings/more indicating if you need to take a break or consulting.

Requires: Python

Supporting:
   [+] gcc/g++ for C/C++

(To Be) Supported Programming Languages:
   [+] Clojure
   [+] Erlang
   [+] Go
   [+] Haskell
   [+] Java
   [+] NodeJS
   [+] Python
   [+] Ruby
   [+] R


Keeping track of stats for you of your code.
[inspired from Zed Shaw's codestats exercise]
